      <description>Want to wake up more beautiful? Yes? Well it&amp;#8217;s time to get acquainted with these three bedtime beauty must-haves. After all, good makeup starts with great skincare! For application tips, watch the step-by-step video tutorial below. Product list! Mary Kay TimeWise Restore and Recover Complex (Normal/Dry). Buy it online at: Mary Kay.com, Mary Kay.co.uk and Mary [...]&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/skincare-product-reviews/bedtime-skincare/"&gt;Bedtime beauty tips!&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog"&gt;Little Miss Makeup&amp;#039;s Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/little-miss-makeups-blog/Little_Miss_Makeups_Blog-Bedtime_beauty_tips.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Want to wake up more beautiful? Yes? Well it&#8217;s time to get acquainted with these three bedtime beauty must-haves.</p>
<p>After all, good makeup starts with great skincare!</p>
<p>For application tips, watch the step-by-step video tutorial below.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ymFAFreRDI"><img src="http://img.youtube.com/vi/3ymFAFreRDI/default.jpg" width="130" height="97" border title="Bedtime beauty tips!" alt="default Bedtime beauty tips!" /></a></p>
<p><span id="more-6719"></span></p>
<p><strong>Product list!</strong></p>
<p>Mary Kay TimeWise Restore and Recover Complex (Normal/Dry). Buy it online at: <a style="text-align: left;" title="MaryKay.com" href="http://www.marykay.com/skincare/agefighting/10041270/10041270/default.aspx">Mary Kay.com</a><span style="text-align: left;">, </span><a style="text-align: left;" title="MaryKay.co.uk" href="http://www.marykay.co.uk/products/skin_care/anti-ageing/timewise_night_restore_and_recover_complex_normal_dry">Mary Kay.co.uk</a><span style="text-align: left;"> and </span><a style="text-align: left;" title="MaryKay.com.au" href="http://www.marykay.com.au/TWNightRestoreRecoverComplexND">Mary Kay.com.au</a><span style="text-align: left;">.</span></p>
<p><img class="alignleft  wp-image-6720" title="Mary Kay TimeWise Night Restore and Recover Complex" src="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Mary-Kay-TimeWise-Night-Restore-and-Recover-Complex-1024x682.jpg" alt="Mary Kay TimeWise Night Restore and Recover Complex 1024x682 Bedtime beauty tips!" width="590" height="393" /></p>
<p>Dior Capture Totale Eyes Essential Eye Zone Boosting Super Serum. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorCaptureTotaleEyesSephora/">Sephora.com</a>, <a title="Selfridges.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorCaptureTotaleEyesSelfridges/">Selfridges.com</a>, or visit your nearest Dior counter.</p>
<p><img class="alignleft  wp-image-6723" title="Dior Capture Totale Eyes Essential Eye Zone Boosting Super Serum" src="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Dior-Capture-Totale-Eyes-Essential-682x1024.jpg" alt="Dior Capture Totale Eyes Essential 682x1024 Bedtime beauty tips!" width="511" height="767" /></p>
<p>Palmer&#8217;s Cocoa Butter Formula Night Renewal Cream. Buy it online at: <a title="Palmers.com" href="http://www.palmers.com/product/detail.php?ID=1128&amp;B=Y&amp;SID=4">Palmers.com</a>, and for stockist information visit: <a title="UKPalmers.com" href="http://uk.palmers.com/product/detail.php?ID=1159&amp;SID=4">UK Palmers.com</a> and <a title="PalmersAustralia.com" href="http://www.palmersaustralia.com/products/face-care/night-renewal-cream/">Palmers Australia.com</a>.</p>
<p><img class="alignleft  wp-image-6725" title="Palmer's Cocoa Butter Formula Night Renewal Cream" src="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Palmers-Cocoa-Butter-Formula-Night-Renewal-Cream-1024x682.jpg" alt="Palmers Cocoa Butter Formula Night Renewal Cream 1024x682 Bedtime beauty tips!" width="590" height="393" /></p>
<div style="text-align: left;"></div>
<p><a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/skincare-product-reviews/bedtime-skincare/">Bedtime beauty tips!</a> is a post from: <a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog">Little Miss Makeup&#039;s Blog</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
