      <description>Is this one of the fairest fall makeup trends of all? I think so. Right now, I&amp;#8217;m mad about fresh, flawless skin and a structured brow, and I love makeup that has an iconic influence and polished finish. For me this look, which was inspired by the Valentino 2012 show, ticks all the boxes. To recreate [...]&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/makeup-application/fall-makeup-trends/"&gt;Ethereal beauty&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog"&gt;Little Miss Makeup&amp;#039;s Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/little-miss-makeups-blog/Little_Miss_Makeups_Blog-Ethereal_beauty.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Is this one of the fairest fall makeup trends of all? I think so. Right now, I&#8217;m mad about fresh, flawless skin and a structured brow, and I love makeup that has an iconic influence and polished finish. For me this look, which was inspired by the Valentino 2012 show, ticks all the boxes.</p>
<p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-6570" title="Valentino Ready-to-Wear Fall 2012" src="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Valentino-Ready-to-Wear-Fall-20121.jpg" alt="Valentino Ready to Wear Fall 20121 Ethereal beauty" width="562" height="843" /></p>
<p>To recreate this look, follow the step-by-step video tutorial below.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O_l-4TaEo20"><img src="http://img.youtube.com/vi/O_l-4TaEo20/default.jpg" width="130" height="97" border title="Ethereal beauty" alt="default Ethereal beauty" /></a></p>
<p><span id="more-6631"></span></p>
<p><strong>Product list!</strong></p>
<p><strong>Preparation.</strong></p>
<p>Cleansing: Johnson&#8217;s Daily Essentials Refreshing Facial Cleansing Wipes. Buy them online at: <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/JohnsonsCleansingWipesBoots/">Boots.com</a>. Available in Australia at leading supermarkets and pharmacies.</p>
<p>Eye serum: Aveeno Positively Radiant Eye Illuminator. Buy it online at: <a title="Aveeno.com" href="http://www.aveeno.com/facialcare/positively-radiant-eye-illuminator">Aveeno.com</a>. For stockists in Australia, visit: <a title="Aveeno.com.au" href="http://www.aveeno.com.au/pages/wheretobuy">Aveeno.com.au</a>.</p>
<p>Moisturizer: Neutrogena Healthy Defence Daily Moisturiser SPF 30 (Combination Oily). For more information, visit: <a title="Neutrogena.com.au" href="http://www.neutrogena.com.au/facial-care/anti-ageing/healthy-defence?filter1=Dry&amp;filter2=Sun_Protection">Neutrogena.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Foundation.</strong></p>
<p>Clarins Ever Matte Foundation in Honey 110. Buy it online at: <a title="Clarins.com" href="http://www.clarinsusa.com/Ever-Matte-SPF-15-Skin-Balancing-Foundation/C050101010,en_US,pd.html?dwvar_C050101010_color=104%20Cream&amp;start=1&amp;cgid=612">Clarins.com</a> and <a title="Clarins.co.uk" href="http://www.clarins.co.uk/Ever%20Matte%20SPF%2015%20OIL-FREE/C050101010,en_GB,pd.html&amp;cgid=612&amp;start=1&amp;dwvar_C050101010_color=103%20Ivory">Clarins.co.uk</a>, or visit your nearest Clarins counter.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Manicare Make-up Wedges</em>. <em>Available in Australia at Priceline and Myer.</em></p>
<p><strong>Concealer.</strong></p>
<p>Givenchy Mister Light Instant Light Corrective Pen in Toast 03. Buy it online at: <a title="Givenchy.com" href="http://www.givenchybeauty.com/item/Mister%20Light" rel="nofollow">Givenchy.com</a>, <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/GivenchyMisterLightSephora/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a> and <a title="Givenchy.com.au" href="http://www.givenchy.com.au/eboutique.html?page=shop.browse&amp;category_id=126&amp;parent_category=122">Givenchy.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: <a title="No7 Concealer Brush by Lisa Eldridge" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/BootsNo7ConcealerBrush/" rel="nofollow">No7 Concealer Brush by Lisa Eldridge</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>Eyeshadow.</strong></p>
<p>Base: Clarins Ever Matte Mineral Powder Compact in Transparent Opal 00. Buy it online at: <a title="Clarins.com" href="http://www.clarinsusa.com/Ever-Matte-Shine-Control-Mineral-Powder-Compact/C050103012,en_US,pd.html?dwvar_C050103012_color=01%20Transparent%20fair&amp;start=7&amp;cgid=613">Clarins.com</a>, <a title="Clarins.co.uk" href="http://www.clarins.co.uk/Ever%20Matte%20Mineral%20Powder%20Compact/C050103012,en_GB,pd.html?dwvar_C050103012_color=00%20Transparent%20opal&amp;start=1&amp;cgid=613">Clarins.co.uk</a> and <a title="Clarins.com.au" href="http://www.adorebeauty.com.au/clarins/clarins-ever-matte-shine-control-mineral-powder-compact.html">AdoreBeauty.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><em><em>Applied to the eyelid and brow bone with</em>: <em>Bobbi Brown Eye Blender Brush. Buy it online at: <a title="BobbiBrown.com" href="http://www.bobbibrowncosmetics.com/product/2281/7658/Brushes-etc/Brushes-and-Tools/Eyes/Eye-Blender-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.com</a>, <a title="BobbiBrown.co.uk" href="http://www.bobbibrown.co.uk/products/spp/index.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT2281&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD7658" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.co.uk</a> and <a title="BobbiBrown.com.au" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/BobbiBrownBlenderBrushAu/" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.com.au</a>.</em></em></p>
<p>Matte purple and matte lilac shadows (right-hand side and bottom) from the <a title="SAX Cosmetics Eye Luxe Quintette in Media Darling 15" href="http://www.saxcosmetics.com/htmls/makeup/eyes/eye_product_info_pages/eyeshadowinfo.html#">SAX Cosmetics Eye Luxe Quintette in Media Darling 15</a>.</p>
<p><em>Blended over the eyelid and through the crease with: MAC Tapered Blending Brush 224. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/145/265/224-Tapered-Blending-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT21842&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD66063" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/265/224-Tapered-Blending-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></p>
<p><em>Applied along the lower lash line with: MAC Mini Shader Brush 228. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/145/275/228-Mini-Shader-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT21842&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD66064" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/275/228-Mini-Shader-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></p>
<p>Metallic mauve shadow (left-hand side) from the <a title="SAX Cosmetics Eye Luxe Quintette in Media Darling 15" href="http://www.saxcosmetics.com/htmls/makeup/eyes/eye_product_info_pages/eyeshadowinfo.html#">SAX Cosmetics Eye Luxe Quintette in Media Darling 15</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied over the outer corner of the eyelid and along the lash lines with: <em>MAC Medium Angled Shading Brush 275. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/145/290/275-Medium-Angled-Shading-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT21842&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD66075" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/290/275-Medium-Angled-Shading-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></em></p>
<p><em>Blended over the outer corner of the eye with: MAC Tapered Blending Brush 224. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/145/265/224-Tapered-Blending-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT21842&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD66063" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/265/224-Tapered-Blending-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>Eye pencil.</strong></p>
<p><a title="SAX Cosmetics Créme Eye Definer in Black 11" href="http://www.saxcosmetics.com/htmls/makeup/eyes/eye_product_info_pages/definereyelinerinfo.html">SAX Cosmetics Créme Eye Definer in Black 11</a>.</p>
<p><em>Blended with: MAC Pencil Brush 219. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/145/386/219-Pencil-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT21842&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD66133" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> or <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/386/219-Pencil-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>Mascara.</strong></p>
<p><a title="Face of Australia Glamourous Lashes Mascara" href="http://www.faceofaustralia.com.au/products/eyes/glamorous-lashes-mascara.aspx">Face of Australia Glamourous Lashes Mascara</a> in Black.</p>
<p><strong>Brows.</strong></p>
<p>Lightest brow powder (top right) from the <a title="SAX Cosmetics Perfect Brow Kit" href="http://www.saxcosmetics.com/htmls/gifts/browKitInfo.html">SAX Cosmetics Perfect Brow Kit</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Small angled brush supplied in the above mentioned kit.</em></p>
<p><em>Brows brushed upward with: <a title="Chanel Brow/Lash Brush" href="http://www.chanel.com/en_AU/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Eye-brushes-PINCEAU-BROSSE-SOURCILS-N%C2%B011-113493" rel="nofollow">Chanel Brow/Lash Brush</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>Face powder.</strong></p>
<p>Clarins Ever Matte Mineral Powder Compact in Transparent Opal 00. Buy it online at: <a title="Clarins.com" href="http://www.clarinsusa.com/Ever-Matte-Shine-Control-Mineral-Powder-Compact/C050103012,en_US,pd.html?dwvar_C050103012_color=01%20Transparent%20fair&amp;start=7&amp;cgid=613">Clarins.com</a>, <a title="Clarins.co.uk" href="http://www.clarins.co.uk/Ever%20Matte%20Mineral%20Powder%20Compact/C050103012,en_GB,pd.html?dwvar_C050103012_color=00%20Transparent%20opal&amp;start=1&amp;cgid=613">Clarins.co.uk</a> and <a title="Clarins.com.au" href="http://www.adorebeauty.com.au/clarins/clarins-ever-matte-shine-control-mineral-powder-compact.html">AdoreBeauty.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Artiste Professional by Manicare Rounded Powder Brush. <em>Available in Australia at Priceline and Myer.</em></em></p>
<p><strong>Lip balm.</strong></p>
<p>Softlips Tinted Lip Conditioner in Pearl. For more information, visit: <a title="SoftLips.com" href="http://www.softlips.com/">Soft Lips.com</a>, <a title="SoftLips.co.uk" href="http://www.softlips.co.uk/">Soft Lips.co.uk</a> and <a title="SoftLips.com.au" href="http://www.softlips.com.au/">Soft Lips.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Artiste Professional by Manicare Lip Brush. <em>Available in Australia at Priceline and Myer.</em></em></p>
<p><strong>Blush.</strong></p>
<p>Rimmel London 3 in 1 Powder Blush in Autumn Catwalk. For stockist information, visit: <a title="Rimmel London UK" href="http://rimmel.rimmellondon.com/wheretobuyuk/" rel="nofollow">Rimmel London UK</a> and <a title="Rimmel London Australia" href="http://www.rimmellondon.com/au/wheretobuy/" rel="nofollow">Rimmel London Australia</a>.</p>
<p>Applied with: <em>Artiste Professional by Manicare Stippling Brush. Available in Australia at Priceline and Myer.</em></p>
<p><a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/makeup-application/fall-makeup-trends/">Ethereal beauty</a> is a post from: <a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog">Little Miss Makeup&#039;s Blog</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
