      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/?p=6565</guid>
      <description>This look was inspired by the Valentino Ready-to-Wear Fall 2012 show. How would I describe it in six words or less? Really pretty makeup – elegant yet understated. Step-by-step video tutorial coming soon! The backstage references below (which I referred to when I was styling the hair and applying the makeup) were kindly provided by Style.com. Understated [...]&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/makeup-trends-2012/really-pretty-makeup/"&gt;Understated elegance&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog"&gt;Little Miss Makeup&amp;#039;s Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/little-miss-makeups-blog/Little_Miss_Makeups_Blog-Understated_elegance.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>This look was inspired by the Valentino Ready-to-Wear Fall 2012 show. How would I describe it in six words or less? Really pretty makeup – elegant yet understated.</p>
<p>Step-by-step video tutorial coming soon!</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-6567 alignleft" title="Before" src="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Before1.jpg" alt="Before1 Understated elegance" width="524" height="797" /></p>
