      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/?p=6406</guid>
      <description>This look is a translation of the metallic, smoky-eye makeup Keira Knightley recently wore on the red carpet. Her eyes were heavily rimmed with kohl liner and finished with a shimmery shadow; then a pretty pinky-peach lip color was added to complete the look. To recreate this look, watch the step-by-step video tutorial below. PRODUCT [...]&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/makeup-application/red-carpet-makeup/"&gt;Get red-carpet ready!&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog"&gt;Little Miss Makeup&amp;#039;s Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/little-miss-makeups-blog/Little_Miss_Makeups_Blog-Get_red-carpet_ready.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>This look is a translation of the metallic, smoky-eye makeup Keira Knightley recently wore on the red carpet. Her eyes were heavily rimmed with kohl liner and finished with a shimmery shadow; then a pretty pinky-peach lip color was added to complete the look.</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-6425 alignnone" title="Red carpet makeup" src="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Red-carpet-makeup1.jpg" alt="Red carpet makeup1 Get red carpet ready!" width="468" height="702" /></p>
<p>To recreate this look, watch the step-by-step video tutorial below.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uZNNMPChGLg"><img src="http://img.youtube.com/vi/uZNNMPChGLg/default.jpg" width="130" height="97" border title="Get red carpet ready!" alt="default Get red carpet ready!" /></a></p>
<p><span id="more-6406"></span></p>
<p><strong>PRODUCT LIST!</strong></p>
<p><strong>Primer.</strong></p>
<p>Nubo Voile in Transparent 0. Buy it online at <a title="NuboBeauty.com" href="http://www.nubobeauty.com/Voile-(Shade-0,-'Transparent')-12.html" rel="nofollow">Nubo Beauty.com</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Foundation.</strong></p>
<p>Rimmel London Wake Me Up Foundation in Soft Beige 200. For stockist information, visit: <a title="Rimmel London US" href="http://www.rimmellondon.com/us/en/wheretobuyusa/" rel="nofollow">Rimmel London US</a>, <a title="Rimmel London UK" href="http://rimmel.rimmellondon.com/wheretobuyuk/" rel="nofollow">Rimmel London UK</a> and <a title="Rimmel London Australia" href="http://www.rimmellondon.com/au/wheretobuy/" rel="nofollow">Rimmel London Australia</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Dior Foundation Brush. Buy it online at: <a title="Dior.com" href="http://www.dior.com/beauty/usa/en/makeup/accessories/accessories/foundation-brush/py0994710-cbrushes.html" rel="nofollow">Dior.com</a> and <a title="Selfridges.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorFoundationBrushUK/" rel="nofollow">Selfridges.com</a>, or visit your nearest Dior counter.</em></p>
<p><strong>Concealer.</strong></p>
<p>Diorskin Nude Skin Perfecting Hydrating Concealer in Beige 002. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorskinNudeConcealerUS/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a> and <a title="Selfridges.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorskinNudeConcealerUK/" rel="nofollow">Selfridges.com</a>, <em>or visit your nearest Dior counter.</em></p>
<p><em>Applied with: <a title="No7 Concealer Brush by Lisa Eldridge" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/BootsNo7ConcealerBrush/" rel="nofollow">No7 Concealer Brush by Lisa Eldridge</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>Eye Pencil.</strong></p>
<p>Rimmel Exaggerate Waterproof Eye Definer in Noir 26. For stockist information, visit: <a title="Rimmel London US" href="http://www.rimmellondon.com/us/en/wheretobuyusa/" rel="nofollow">Rimmel London US</a>, <a title="Rimmel London UK" href="http://rimmel.rimmellondon.com/wheretobuyuk/" rel="nofollow">Rimmel London UK</a> and <a title="Rimmel London Australia" href="http://www.rimmellondon.com/au/wheretobuy/" rel="nofollow">Rimmel London Australia</a>.</p>
<p><em>Blended with: MAC Pencil Brush 219. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/145/386/219-Pencil-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT21842&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD66133" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> or <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/386/219-Pencil-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>Eyeshadow.</strong></p>
<p>Dark brown shade from Chanel Les 4 Ombres – Quadra Eyeshadow in Mystic Eyes 14. Buy it online at: <a title="Chanel.com" href="http://www.chanel.com/en_US/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Eyeshadow-LES-4-OMBRES-89134" rel="nofollow">Chanel.com</a> and <a title="Selfridges.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/ChanelLes4Ombres/" rel="nofollow">Selfridges.com</a>, or visit the <a title="Store Locator" href="http://www.chanel.com/en_AU/store-locator/search/fragrance-beauty/" rel="nofollow">Chanel Store Locator</a> to find your nearest stockist.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: MAC Pencil Brush 219. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/145/386/219-Pencil-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT21842&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD66133" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> or <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/386/219-Pencil-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></p>
<p><em>Winged-out with: Dior Eyeshadow Brush Medium. Buy it online at: <a title="Dior.com" href="http://www.dior.com/beauty/int/en/makeup/accessories/accessories/y0994305/py0994305.html" rel="nofollow">Dior.com</a> and <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorEyeshadowBrushMediumBoots/" rel="nofollow">Boots.com</a>, or visit your nearest Dior counter.</em></p>
<p>Chanel Poudre Universelle Libre in Naturel 30. Buy it online at: <a title="Chanel.com" href="http://www.chanel.com/en_US/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Powder-POUDRE-UNIVERSELLE-LIBRE-88623" rel="nofollow">Chanel.com</a> and <a title="Selfridges.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/ChanelLoosePowder/" rel="nofollow">Selfridges.com</a>, or visit the <a title="Store Locator" href="http://www.chanel.com/en_AU/store-locator/search/fragrance-beauty/">Chanel Store Locator</a> to find your nearest stockist.</p>
<p><em>Blended over the upper eyelid and over the brow bone with: MAC Tapered Blending Brush 224. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/145/265/224-Tapered-Blending-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT21842&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD66063" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/265/224-Tapered-Blending-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>Eyelash curler.</strong></p>
<p>Shu Uemura Eyelash Curler. Buy it online at: <a title="ShuUemura-USA.com" href="http://www.shuuemura-usa.com/_us/_en/accessories/eyelash-curlers/eyelash-curler.htm" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura-USA.com</a> and <a title="ShuUemura.co.uk" href="http://www.shuuemura.co.uk/accessories/eyelash-curlers/eyelash-curler.aspx" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura.co.uk</a>, or visit <a title="ShuUemura.com" href="http://www.shuuemura.com/" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura.com</a> to find your nearest stockist.</p>
