      <description>&amp;#8220; &amp;#8217;Tonal, monochrome or matchy-matchy&amp;#8217; &amp;#8221; is the perfect way to sum up one of this season&amp;#8217;s hottest makeup looks. To translate the trend, pick a single colorway and apply it to the eyelid, top of the cheekbone and lip. Sunset shades like peach, melon, apricot and marmalade were seen at shows like Jaeger, Preen and DKNY. Choose these hues – [...]&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/makeup-application/spring-makeup-trends/"&gt;Pretty in peach!&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog"&gt;Little Miss Makeup&amp;#039;s Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/little-miss-makeups-blog/Little_Miss_Makeups_Blog-Pretty_in_peach.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>&#8220; &#8217;Tonal, monochrome or matchy-matchy&#8217; &#8221; is the perfect way to sum up one of this season&#8217;s hottest makeup looks. To translate the trend, pick a single colorway and apply it to the eyelid, top of the cheekbone and lip. Sunset shades like peach, melon, apricot and marmalade were seen at shows like Jaeger, Preen and DKNY. Choose these hues – they look fresh, feminine and oh so pretty on everyone!&#8221; LMM, 2012.</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-6060 aligncenter" title="Monochrome makeup" src="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Monochrome-makeup.jpg" alt="Monochrome makeup Pretty in peach!" width="428" height="667" /></p>
<p>To recreate this look, watch the step-by-step video tutorial below.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_BWEh0w5d3w"><img src="http://img.youtube.com/vi/_BWEh0w5d3w/default.jpg" width="130" height="97" border title="Pretty in peach!" alt="default Pretty in peach!" /></a></p>
<p><span id="more-6018"></span></p>
<p><strong>PRODUCT LIST!</strong></p>
<p><strong>Preparation.</strong></p>
<p>Cleanser: Lancôme Eau Micellaire Douceur Express Cleansing Water for Face, Eyes and Lips. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/LancomeCleansingWater/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a> and <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/LancomeCleansingWaterUK/" rel="nofollow">Boots.com</a>, or visit your nearest Lancôme counter.</p>
<p>Moisturizer: Elemis Pro-Collagen Marine Cream. Buy it online at: <a title="TimeToSpa.com" href="http://www.timetospa.com/elemis/elemis-pro-collagen-marine-cream/" rel="nofollow">Time to Spa.com</a> and <a title="TimeToSpa.co.uk" href="http://www.timetospa.co.uk/skincare/moisturisers/elemis-pro-collagen-marine-cream-50ml/" rel="nofollow">Time to Spa.co.uk</a>.</p>
<p>Eye/Lip Cream: Pro-Intense Eye and Lip Contour Cream. Buy it online at: <a title="TimeToSpa.com" href="http://www.timetospa.com/elemis/elemis-pro-intense-eye-and-lip-contour-cream/" rel="nofollow">Time to Spa.com</a> and <a title="TimeToSpa.co.uk" href="http://www.timetospa.co.uk/elemis/eyes-and-lips/New-Elemis-Pro-Intense-Eye-and-Lip-Contour-Cream/" rel="nofollow">Time to Spa.co.uk</a>.</p>
<p>Primer: Shu Uemura UV Under Base Mousse SPF 30 in Beige. Buy it online at: <a title="ShuUemura.co.uk" href="http://www.shuuemura.co.uk/makeup/face/base/uv-under-base-mousse-beige-spf-30.aspx" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura.co.uk</a> and <a title="DavidJones.com.au" href="http://www2.davidjones.com.au/shop-online/product-details.jsp?productID=102927&amp;category=2867927" rel="nofollow">David Jones.com.au</a>, or visit <a title="ShuUemura.com" href="http://www.shuuemura.com" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura.com</a> to find your nearest stockist.</p>
<p><strong>Foundation.</strong></p>
<p>Dior Diorskin Nude Natural Glow Hydrating Makeup in Rosy Beige 032. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorskinNudeFoundationSephora/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a> and <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorskinNudeBoots/" rel="nofollow">Boots.com</a>, or visit your nearest Dior counter.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Chanel Foundation Brush 6. Buy it online at: <a title="Chanel.com" href="http://www.chanel.com/en_US/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Foundation-PINCEAU-FOND-DE-TEINT-122540" rel="nofollow">Chanel.com</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>Concealer/Highlighter Pen.</strong></p>
<p>Lancôme Teint Miracle Concealer Pen in Beige Lumière 03. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/LancomeTeintMiracleRetouchPenSephora/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a> and <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/LancomeTeintMiracleRetouchPenUK/" rel="nofollow">Boots.com</a>, or visit your nearest Lancôme counter.</p>
<p><strong>Eyeshadow.</strong></p>
<p>Peach: MAC Eye Shadow in Samoa Silk. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/154/363/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/shaded/154/363/templatesproductsproductslandingtmpl/templatesproductscategorytmpl/templatesproductsmptmpl/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/shaded/154/363/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><em>Pressed onto the eyelid with: <em>Dior Eyeshadow Brush Medium. Buy it online at: <a title="Dior.com" href="http://www.dior.com/beauty/int/en/makeup/accessories/accessories/y0994305/py0994305.html" rel="nofollow">Dior.com</a> and <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorEyeshadowBrushMediumBoots/" rel="nofollow">Boots.com</a>.</em></em></p>
<p><em><em>Blended with</em>: <em>Bobbi Brown Eye Blender Brush. Buy it online at: <a title="BobbiBrown.com" href="http://www.bobbibrowncosmetics.com/product/2281/7658/Brushes-etc/Brushes-and-Tools/Eyes/Eye-Blender-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.com</a>, <a title="BobbiBrown.co.uk" href="http://www.bobbibrown.co.uk/products/spp/index.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT2281&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD7658" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.co.uk</a> and <a title="BobbiBrown.com.au" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/BobbiBrownBlenderBrushAu/" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.com.au</a>.</em></em></p>
<p>Pinky-peach: Top left shade from the Dior 5-Couleur palette in Rosy Tan 754. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/Dior5CouleurEyeshadowSephora/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a> and <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/Dior5CouleurUK/" rel="nofollow">Boots.com</a>, or visit your nearest Dior counter.</p>
<p><em><em>Applied to the eyelid and top of the cheekbone with</em>: <em>Bobbi Brown Eye Blender Brush. Buy it online at: <a title="BobbiBrown.com" href="http://www.bobbibrowncosmetics.com/product/2281/7658/Brushes-etc/Brushes-and-Tools/Eyes/Eye-Blender-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.com</a>, <a title="BobbiBrown.co.uk" href="http://www.bobbibrown.co.uk/products/spp/index.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT2281&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD7658" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.co.uk</a> and <a title="BobbiBrown.com.au" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/BobbiBrownBlenderBrushAu/" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.com.au</a>.</em></em></p>
<p><em>Both eyeshadows blended beneath the eye with: <em>MAC Medium Angled Shading Brush 275. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/145/290/275-Medium-Angled-Shading-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT21842&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD66075" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/290/275-Medium-Angled-Shading-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></em></p>
<p><strong>Mascara.</strong></p>
<p>Dior Diorshow New Look Mascara in Black. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorshowNewLookMascaraUS/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a>, <a title="Selfridges.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorshowNewLookMascaraUK/" rel="nofollow">Selfridges.com</a>, or visit your nearest Dior counter.</p>
<p><strong>Lipstick.</strong></p>
<p>Dior Addict Extreme Lipstick in Riviera 639. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/DiorAddictExtremeLipstickUS/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a>, or visit your nearest Dior counter.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Shu Uemura Natural Lip Brush 6 M. <em>Buy it online at: <a title="ShuUemura.co.uk" href="http://www.shuuemura.co.uk/accessories/makeup-brushes/lip-brushes/natural-brush-6m.aspx" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura.co.uk</a>, or visit <a title="ShuUemura.com" href="http://www.shuuemura.com/" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura.com</a> to find your nearest stockist.</em></em></p>
<p><strong>Blush.</strong></p>
<p>MAC Eye Shadow in Samoa Silk. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/154/363/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/shaded/154/363/templatesproductsproductslandingtmpl/templatesproductscategorytmpl/templatesproductsmptmpl/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/shaded/154/363/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>. And, the top left shade from the Dior 5-Couleur palette in Rosy Tan 754. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/Dior5CouleurEyeshadowSephora/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a> and <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/Dior5CouleurUK/" rel="nofollow">Boots.com</a>, or visit your nearest Dior counter.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: MAC Small Contour Brush 109. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/146/826/109-Small-Contour-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/146/826/Brushes/Face/109-Small-Contour-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and<a title=" MACCosmetics.com.au." href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/146/826/109-Small-Contour-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow"> MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>Brows.</strong></p>
<p><em>Brows brushed upward with: <a title="Chanel Brow/Lash Brush" href="http://www.chanel.com/en_AU/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Eye-brushes-PINCEAU-BROSSE-SOURCILS-N%C2%B011-113493" rel="nofollow">Chanel Brow/Lash Brush</a>.</em></p>
