      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/?p=5842</guid>
      <description>“There were strong references to the 1950s in the S/S 12 shows, both in the fashion and the faces. While the look below gives a nod to the decade, it’s more of a modern interpretation than a literal one. This ’50s makeup look is fashion forward, feminine and gorgeously glam. The dewy complexion is one of its [...]&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/makeup-application/50s-makeup/"&gt;A modern take on 1950s glamour&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog"&gt;Little Miss Makeup&amp;#039;s Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/little-miss-makeups-blog/Little_Miss_Makeups_Blog-A_modern_take_on_1950s_glamour.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>“There were strong references to the 1950s in the S/S 12 shows, both in the fashion and the faces. While the look below gives a nod to the decade, it’s more of a modern interpretation than a literal one. This ’50s makeup look is fashion forward, feminine and gorgeously glam. The dewy complexion is one of its main features. I drew inspiration from shows like Nina Ricci, Rochas, Stella McCartney, Valentino, Chloe, Jil Sander, Versace, Dolce &amp; Gabbana, Prada and Versus, where dreamy, lunar-skinned ladies sashayed down the runway. Bouffant-style hairdos are also big this season (as seen on the catwalk at Fendi and Jil Sander). That’s definitely a cue to dust off your volumizing products and bust out a bit of backcombing action!” LMM, 2012.</p>
<p><img class="alignleft  wp-image-5893" title="50s makeup" src="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/50s-makeup-682x1024.jpg" alt="50s makeup 682x1024 A modern take on 1950s glamour" width="546" height="819" /></p>
<p><em>LMM says: Wear this new-season trend on a Valentine&#8217;s Day date with your darling. It&#8217;s guaranteed to make his heart go thumpety-thump!</em></p>
<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to recreate this look, watch the video tutorial below.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H3Z7NaM0VNE"><img src="http://img.youtube.com/vi/H3Z7NaM0VNE/default.jpg" width="130" height="97" border title="A modern take on 1950s glamour" alt="default A modern take on 1950s glamour" /></a></p>
<p><span id="more-5842"></span></p>
<p><strong>PRODUCT LIST!</strong></p>
<p><strong>PREPARATION.</strong></p>
<p>Cleanser: Lancôme Eau Micellaire Douceur Express Cleansing Solution for Face, Eyes and Lips. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/LancomeCleansingWater/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a> and <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/LancomeCleansingWaterUK/" rel="nofollow">Boots.com</a>, or visit your nearest Lancôme counter.</p>
<p>Moisturizer: Nubo Cell Dynamic Day Performance SPF 20. Buy it online at: <a title="Nubo Beauty.com" href="http://www.nubobeauty.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=2_12&amp;products_id=5" rel="nofollow">Nubo Beauty.com</a>.</p>
<p>Eye cream: Nutrimetics Restore Anti-Ageing Firming Eye Crème. Buy it online at: <a title="Nutrimetics.com.au" href="http://www.nutrimetics.com.au/portal/skincare/anti-ageing/11970_promo.html" rel="nofollow">Nutrimetics.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><strong>FOUNDATION.</strong></p>
<p>Lancôme Teint Miracle Foundation in Beige Nature 04. Buy it online at: <a title="Sephora.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/LancomeTeintMiracleFoundationSephora/" rel="nofollow">Sephora.com</a>, <a title="Selfridges.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/LancomeTeintMiracleFoundationSelfridges/" rel="nofollow">Selfridges.com</a> and <a title="AdoreBeauty.com.au" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/LancomeTeintMiracleFoundationAu/" rel="nofollow"> Adore Beauty.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Lancôme Foundation Brush. Buy it online at: <a title="Lancome-USA.com" href="http://www.lancome-usa.com/Foundation---Brush-%232/990361,default,pd.html?start=2&amp;q=foundation%20brush" rel="nofollow">Lancome-USA.com</a>, or visit your nearest Lancôme counter.</em></p>
<p><strong>CONCEALER AND HIGHLIGHTER.</strong></p>
<p>Under-eye area: Maybelline Instant Age Rewind Eraser in Light 120. Buy it online at: <a title="Drugstore.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/MaybellineInstantAgeRewindEraserUS/" rel="nofollow">Drugstore.com</a>. Available in Australia at: Priceline, Target, Big W, Kmart, Coles and Woolworths.</p>
<p>Around nose: MAC Studio Finish Concealer in NC30. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/157/314/Studio-Finish-SPF-35-Concealer/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a> and <a title="Selfridges.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/MACStudioFinishConcealerSelfridges/" rel="nofollow">Selfridges.com</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Shu Uemura Eye Brush Synthetic 10. <em>Buy it online at: <a title="ShuUemura-USA.com" href="http://www.shuuemura-usa.com/_us/_en/accessories/makeup-brushes/eye/synthetic-brush-10.htm" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura-USA.com</a></em> and <a title="ShuUemura.co.uk" href="http://www.shuuemura.co.uk/accessories/makeup-brushes/eye-brushes/synthetic-brush-10.aspx" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura.co.uk</a></em>, <em>or visit <a title="ShuUemura.com" href="http://www.shuuemura.com" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura.com</a> to find your nearest stockist.</em></p>
<p><strong>LIP BALM.</strong></p>
<p>The Lip Balm by La Mer. Buy it online at: <a title="CremeDeLaMer.com" href="http://www.cremedelamer.com/templates/products/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CATEGORY5783&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD2464" rel="nofollow">Creme De La Mer.com</a>, <a title="Selfridges.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/LaMerLipBalmUK/" rel="nofollow">Selfridges.com</a> and <a title="CremeDeLaMer.com.au" href="http://www.cremedelamer.com.au/templates/products/sp_nonshaded.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT7080&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD75927" rel="nofollow">Creme De La Mer.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: <a title="Chanel Pinceau Correcteur 8" href="http://www.chanel.com/en_AU/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Complexion-brushes-PETIT-PINCEAU-CORRECTEUR-N%C2%B08-113464" rel="nofollow">Chanel Pinceau Correcteur 8</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>EYESHADOW.</strong></p>
<p>Base: Bobbi Brown Long-Wear Cream Shadow in Sand Dollar.  Buy it online at: <a title="BobbiBrownCosmetics.com" href="http://www.bobbibrowncosmetics.com/product/2331/8195/Makeup/Eyes/Long-Wear/Long-Wear-Cream-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="Bobbi Brown.co.uk" href="http://www.bobbibrown.co.uk/product/2331/8195/Makeup/Eyes/Long-Wear/Long-Wear-Cream-Shadow/Award-Winner/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.co.uk</a> and <a title="BobbiBrown.com.au" href="http://www.bobbibrown.com.au/product/2331/8195/Long-Wear-Cream-Shadow/Award-Winner/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.com.au</a>.</p>
<p>Eyelid: Bobbi Brown Metallic Long-Wear Cream Shadow in Goldstone. Buy it online at: <a title="BobbiBrownCosmetics.com" href="http://www.bobbibrowncosmetics.com/product/2330/7631/Makeup/Eyes/Eye-Shadows/Metallic-Long-Wear-Cream-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="Bobbi Brown.co.uk" href="http://www.bobbibrown.co.uk/product/2330/7631/Makeup/Eyes/Eye-Shadows/Metallic-Long-Wear-Cream-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.co.uk</a> and <a title="BobbiBrown.com.au" href="http://www.bobbibrown.com.au/product/2330/7631/Metallic-Long-Wear-Cream-Shadow/Best-Seller/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Shu Uemura Eye Brush Synthetic 10. <em>Buy it online at: <a title="ShuUemura-USA.com" href="http://www.shuuemura-usa.com/_us/_en/accessories/makeup-brushes/eye/synthetic-brush-10.htm" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura-USA.com</a></em> and <a title="ShuUemura.co.uk" href="http://www.shuuemura.co.uk/accessories/makeup-brushes/eye-brushes/synthetic-brush-10.aspx" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura.co.uk</a></em>, <em>or visit <a title="ShuUemura.com" href="http://www.shuuemura.com" rel="nofollow">Shu Uemura.com</a> to find your nearest stockist.</em></p>
<p>Lower lash line: Bobbi Brown Long-Wear Cream Shadow in Sand Dollar. Buy it online at: <a title="BobbiBrownCosmetics.com" href="http://www.bobbibrowncosmetics.com/product/2331/8195/Makeup/Eyes/Long-Wear/Long-Wear-Cream-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="Bobbi Brown.co.uk" href="http://www.bobbibrown.co.uk/product/2331/8195/Makeup/Eyes/Long-Wear/Long-Wear-Cream-Shadow/Award-Winner/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.co.uk</a> and <a title="BobbiBrown.com.au" href="http://www.bobbibrown.com.au/product/2331/8195/Long-Wear-Cream-Shadow/Award-Winner/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Bobbi Brown.com.au</a>, and Gorgeous Cosmetics Shimmer Dust in Suede. Buy it online at: <a title="GorgeousCosmetics.com" href="http://gorgeouscosmetics.com/store/product.php?productid=18089&amp;cat=506&amp;page=1" rel="nofollow">Gorgeous Cosmetics.com</a>.</p>
<p><em>Blended with: MAC Medium Angled Shading Brush 275. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/145/290/275-Medium-Angled-Shading-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/spp.tmpl?CATEGORY_ID=CAT21842&amp;PRODUCT_ID=PROD66075" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/290/275-Medium-Angled-Shading-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC</a></em><em><a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/145/290/275-Medium-Angled-Shading-Brush/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">Cosmetics.com.au</a></em>.</p>
<p><strong>EYELINER.</strong></p>
<p>Face of Australia Liquid Eyeliner in Black. Find a stockist at: <a title="FaceOfAustralia.com.au" href="http://www.faceofaustralia.com.au/products/eyes/liquid-eyeliner.aspx" rel="nofollow">Face Of Australia.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><em>Blended with:</em> <em>ELF Studio Small Smudge Brush. Buy it online at: <a title="ELFCosmetics.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/elfStudioSmudgeBrush/" rel="nofollow">ELF Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="EyesLipsFace.co.uk" href="http://www.eyeslipsface.co.uk/product~prodID~134.htm" rel="nofollow">Eyes Lips Face.co.uk</a> and <a title="ELFCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.elfcosmetics.com.au/products/e-l-f-studio-small-smudge-brush" rel="nofollow">ELF Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>MASCARA.</strong></p>
<p>Maybelline Volum&#8217;Express One by One Mascara in Brownish Black 256. Buy it online at: <a title="Drugstore.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/MaybellineVolumeExpressOneByOneUS/" rel="nofollow">Drugstore.com</a> and <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/MaybellineVolumeExpressOneByOneUK/" rel="nofollow">Boots.com</a>. Available in Australia at: Priceline, Target, Big W, Kmart, Coles and Woolworths.</p>
<p><strong>BROWS.</strong></p>
<p>MAC Eye Shadow in Omega. Buy it online at: <a title="MACCosmetics.com" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/154/363/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="MACCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.maccosmetics.co.uk/product/shaded/154/363/templatesproductsproductslandingtmpl/templatesproductscategorytmpl/templatesproductsmptmpl/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.co.uk</a> and <a title="MACCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.maccosmetics.com.au/product/shaded/154/363/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl" rel="nofollow">MAC Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</p>
<p><em>Applied with: Prescriptives Eye Shaper Brush.</em></p>
<p><em>Gaps filled in with: ELF Studio Small Angled Brush. Buy it online at: <a title="ELFCosmetics.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/elfStudioSmallAngledBrush/" rel="nofollow">ELF Cosmetics.com</a>, <a title="ELFCosmetics.co.uk" href="http://www.eyeslipsface.co.uk/product~prodID~143.htm" rel="nofollow">Eyes Lips Face.co.uk</a> and <a title="ELFCosmetics.com.au" href="http://www.elfcosmetics.com.au/products/e-l-f-studio-small-angled-brush" rel="nofollow">ELF Cosmetics.com.au</a>.</em></p>
<p><em>Brows brushed upward with: <a title="Chanel Brow/Lash Brush" href="http://www.chanel.com/en_AU/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Eye-brushes-PINCEAU-BROSSE-SOURCILS-N%C2%B011-113493" rel="nofollow">Chanel Brow/Lash Brush</a>.</em></p>
<p><strong>LIP COLOR.</strong></p>
<p>Maybelline Color Sensational The Shine lipsticks in Rosy Dream 109 and Juicy Bubblegum 140. Buy them online at: <a title="Drugstore.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/MaybellineHighShineUS/" rel="nofollow">Drugstore.com</a> and <a title="Boots.com" href="http://littlemissmakeup.com/blog/MaybellineHighShineUK/" rel="nofollow">Boots.com</a>. Available in Australia at: Priceline, Target, Big W, Kmart, Coles and Woolworths. (Note: The color range differs between countries.)</p>
<p><em>Applied with: <em>Chanel Pinceau Correcteur. Buy it online at: <a title="Chanel.com" href="http://www.chanel.com/en_US/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Face-PINCEAU-CORRECTEUR-122532" rel="nofollow">Chanel.com</a></em>.</em></p>
